_source.text: A Darkened with Umbrae who hits Morality 0 dies and becomes a Darkspawn , a monster whose only impulse is to serve the Dark...which is far better than those who don't have Umbrae, who become Mnemosyne who retain their bodies and intellects... and nothing else .
